Sentencas: It is found that the solid solubility of Ce in Nd2-xCeCuO4 +/-delta is limited up to x=0.2.

Sentencas: /-delta is thermodynamically and chemically stable against gadolinia-doped ceria (GDC) up to 1200 degrees C. On the other hand, it reacts with a yttria-stabilized zirconia electrolyte to form Nd2Zr2O7.
Titulo: Combustion synthesized Nd2-xCexCuO4 (x=0-0.25) cathode materials for intermediate temperature solid oxide fuel cell applications

Sentencas: At 700 degrees C, the ASR of a Nd1.8Ce0.2CuO4 +/-delta/GDC/Nd1.8Ce0.2CuO4 +/-delta cell sintered at 800 degrees C is 0.13 ohm cm(2), and the ASR proportionally improves with increase in the sintering temperature of the electrochemical cell.
Titulo: Combustion synthesized Nd2-xCexCuO4 (x=0-0.25) cathode materials for intermediate temperature solid oxide fuel cell applications

Sentencas: The improved ASR and electrochemical performance are attributed to the nanocrystalline nature of the cathode material.
